Last updated: November 9, 2025

VoxLead.Agency provides AI-powered appointment and messaging automation for service businesses.  
We respect your privacy and collect only necessary data to deliver these services.

## Information We Collect
- Contact info (name, phone, email) submitted during bookings or demos.
- Business info (clinic name, city, niche) for setup.
- Communication data (calls, SMS) processed via Twilio for appointment confirmations.

## How We Use Information
- To send booking confirmations, reminders, and updates.
- To improve system accuracy and response quality.
- We never sell or share data with third parties for marketing.

## Data Retention
Data is securely stored and retained only as long as necessary for service operations.

## Opt-Out
Users can stop receiving SMS anytime by replying **STOP**.

